aa%20baap%20se%20bana%20ke%20rakho%20bhai%20koi%20zarurat%20nahi%20hai%20independent%20hone%20ke%20liye%20ghar%20se%20bhaagne%20ki%20(One%20can%20get%201%20BHK%20for%20Rs.%2050-70%2C00%20in%20Mumbai.%20Be%20on%20good%20terms%20with%20your%20mom%20and%20dad%2C%20no%20need%20to%20rush%20out%20of%20your%20house%20to%20be%20independent)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20the%20tweet%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E1%20bhk%2050-70%20hazar%20ka%20mil%20raha%20hai%20mumbai%20mein%20maa%20baap%20se%20bana%20ke%20rakho%20bhai%20koi%20zarurat%20nahi%20hai%20independent%20hone%20ke%20liye%20ghar%20se%20bhaagne%20ki%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20vita%20(%40kebabandcoke)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkebabandcoke%2Fstatus%2F1799418837429113235%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20posted%2C%20the%20tweet%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20triggering%20a%20debate.%20While%20some%20found%20her%20post%20relatable%20and%20narrated%20similar%20struggles%2C%20others%20suggested%20a%20few%20localities%20where%20the%20flats%20were%20said%20to%20be%20available%20at%20a%20lesser%20price.%20One%20user%20wrote%2C%20''True%2C%20inflation%20is%20outpacing%20the%20salaries%20at%20a%20very%20fast%20speed.%20Getting%20a%20house%2C%20good%20healthcare%20%26amp%3B%20quality%20education%20without%20a%20big%20burden%20of%20loan%20seems%20like%20an%20impossible%20dream%20to%20many.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20''My%20favourite%20part%20of%20this%20tweet%20is%20people%20trying%20to%20suggest%20cheaper%20locations%20to%20you.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20said%2C%20''TBH%2C%2050-70k%201bhk%20shouldn't%20be%20the%20only%20reason%20for%20living%20with%20mom%20and%20dad.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20st