DU)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPopularly%20known%20as%20Lalan%20Singh%2C%20the%20Bhumihar%20leader%20has%20been%20among%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20closest%20aides%20for%20years.%20Mentored%20by%20socialist%20icon%20Karpoori%20Thakur%2C%20Lalan%20Singh%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20stitching%20the%20JDU-RJD%20alliance%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKinjarapu%20Ram%20Mohan%20Naidu%20(TDP)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHe%20is%20among%20the%20two%20TDP%20leaders%20who%20have%20been%20assigned%20ministerial%20berths%2C%20but%20the%20only%20one%20to%20get%20a%20cabinet%20rank.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20youngest%20in%20the%20council%20of%20ministers.%20His%20father%20KY%20Naidu%20had%20served%20as%20a%20Union%20minister%20during%201996-98.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20has%20won%2016%20seats%2C%20the%20second-best%20performance%20by%20a%20party%20in%20the%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchirag-paswan-solidifies-status-as-real-political-heir-of-father-ram-vilas-5853391%5C%22%3EChirag%20Paswan%3C%2Fa%3E%20(LJPRV)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20young%20leader%20from%20Bihar%20heads%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%2C%20which%20has%20won%20five%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20The%20former%20actor%20has%20been%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Parliament%20twice%20in%20the%20past%2C%20but%20it's%20the%20first%20time%20he%20has%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Union%20cabinet.%20Chirag%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%2C%20who%20led%20the%20consumer%20affairs%20ministry%20until%20his%20death%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMinisters%20of%20State%20(Independent%20charge)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fonce-bjps-political-rival-jayant-chaudhary-joins-modi-3-0-cabinet-5854291%5C%22%3EJayant%20Chaudhary%3C%2Fa%3E%20(RLD)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMr%20Chaudhary%20was%20once%20a%20political%20rival%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20aligned%20his%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20with%20the%20NDA%20in%20March%2C%20and%20now%20is%20part%20of%20Modi%203.0.%20He%20is%20the%20grandson%20of%20former%20prime%20minister%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20awarded%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20the%20highest%20civilian%20honour%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrataprao%20Ganpatrao%20Jadhav%20(Shiv%20Sena)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHe%20is%20the%20only%20leader%20from%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20in%20the%20Union%20Council%20of%20ministers.%20The%20four-time%20MP%20had%20served%20as%20a%20minister%20of%20state%20in%20Maharashtra%20governments%20led%20by%20Manohar%20Joshi%20and%20Narayan%20Rane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch1%3E%3Cstrong%3EMinisters%20of%20State%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh1%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERamdas%20Athawale%20(RPIA)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHe%20heads%20the%20Republican%20Party%20of%20India%20-%20Athawale%2C%20a%20party%20with%20its%20roots%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20Federation%20founded%20by%20BR%20Ambedkar.%20He%20was%20the%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Social%20Justice%20in%20the%20previous%20Modi%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERam%20Nath%20Thakur%20(JDU)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERam%20Nath%20Thakur%20is%20a%20key%20face%20in%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20Janata%20Dal-United.%20He%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Karpoori%20Thakur%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar%20who%20was%20recently%20awarded%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna.%20He%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnupriya%20Patel%20(Apna%20Dal%20Soneylal)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20representative%20from%20Mirzapur%20heads%20the%20Apna%20Dal%20(Soneylal)%2C%20a%20breakaway%20group%20of%20Apna%20Dal%20that%20was%20formed%20by%20her%20father%20Sone%20Lal%20Patel.%20Ms%20Patel%20was%20a%20Minister%20of%20State%20in%20Commerce%20and%20Health%20ministries%20in%20the%20previous%20two%20Modi%20cabinets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3