dnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcentral-african-republic-government-suspends-chinese-mining-company-for-alleged-ties-to-armed-groups%2Famp_articleshow%2F110861096.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcentral-african-republic-government-suspends-chinese-mining-company-for-alleged-ties-to-armed-groups%2Famp_articleshow%2F110861096.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Mumbai%20Airport%20Scare%2C%20IndiGo%20And%20Air%20India%20Planes%20Were%20Just%20509%20m%20Apart%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20Mumbai's%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20International%20Airport%2C%20two%20aircraft%20came%20alarmingly%20close%20to%20each%20other%20on%20the%20runway%20yesterday%2C%20with%20only%20509%20metres%20separating%20them.%20An%20IndiGo%20flight%20from%20Indore%20landed%20on%20the%20same%20runway%20just%20moments%20after%20an%20Air%20India%20jet%20took%20off%20for%20Thiruvananthapuram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(DGCA)%20has%20launched%20an%20investigation%20and%20de-rostered%20the%20air%20traffic%20controller%20involved%20in%20the%20incident.%20According%20to%20DGCA%20guidelines%2C%20air%20traffic%20control%20can%20issue%20landing%20clearance%20only%20when%20there%20is%20a%20reasonable%20assurance%20that%20the%20landing%20aircraft%20won't%20cross%20the%20threshold%20until%20the%20preceding%20departing%20aircraft%20has%20crossed%20the%20end%20of%20the%20runway.%20This%20rule%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20violated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20particular%20case%20that%20happened%20on%20Saturday%20at%20the%20Mumbai%20airport%2C%20the%20visibility%20was%20good%20and%20there%20was%20no%20air%20proximity%20situation%20in%20respect%20to%20the%20landing%20of%20the%20IndiGo%20flight%20and%20the%20taking%20off%20of%20the%20Air%20India%20flight%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20guild%20representing%20air%20traffic%20controllers%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20from%20Flightradar%20contradicts%20the%20Air%20Traffic%20Controllers'%20Guild's%20assertion%20that%20there%20was%20no%20air%20proximity%20issue.%20The%20video%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%20shows%20the%20Air%20India%20jet%20taking%20off%20while%20the%20IndiGo%20plane%20lands%20on%20the%20same%20runway%2C%20raising%20serious%20safety%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndiGo%20and%20Air%20India%2C%20in%20their%20respective%20statements%2C%20said%20that%20their%20pilots%20followed%20ATC%20instructions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20June%208%2C%202024%2C%20IndiGo%20flight%206E%206053%20from%20Indore%20was%20given%20landing%20clearance%20by%20ATC%20at%20Mumbai%20Airport.%20The%20Pilot%20in%20Command%20continued%20the%20approach%20and%20landing%2C%20following%20ATC%20instructions.%20At%20IndiGo%2C%20passenger%20safety%20is%20paramount%2C%20and%20we%20have%20reported%20the%20incident%20as%20per%20procedure%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20IndiGo%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Air%20India%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3BAI657%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Trivandrum%20was%20on%20take-off%20roll%20on%20June%208.%20The%20Air%20India%20aircraft%20was%20cleared%20by%20Air%20Traffic%20Control%20to%20enter%20the%20runway%20and%20subsequently%20cleared%20for%20take-off.%20The%20Air%20India%20aircraft%20continued%20with%20the%20take-off%20movement%20in%20accordance%20with%20laid%20down%20procedures.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20reassurances%2C%20the%20incident%20has%20brought%20to%20light%20the%20intense%20pressure%20faced%20by%20air%20traffic%20controllers%20at%20high-density%20airports%20like%20Mumbai.%20The%20airport%2C%20a%20single-runway%20operation%20with%20crossing%20runways%2009%2F27%20and%2014%2F32%2C%20handles%20over%20850%20flights%20per%20day%2C%20with%20around%2046%20arrivals%20and%20departures%20per%20hour%20on%20runway%2027%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DGCA's%20ongoing%20probe%20aims%20to%20determine%20whether%20all%20norms%20were%20followed%20by%20the%20ATC%20and%20the%20pilots%20involved.%20The%20Guild%20also%20highlighted%20the%20high%20stress%20and%20pressure%20faced%20by%20ATCs%20during%20peak%20traffic%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20airport%20had%20earlier%20announced%20plans%20to%20handle%208%20per%20cent%20more%20air%20traffic%20during%20the%20summer%20schedule%2C%20increasing%20operations%20to%20951%20flights%20per%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717992420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F15keseug_mumbai-airport-close-call_625x300_09_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-mumbai-airport-scare-indigo-and-air-india-planes-were-just-509-m-apart-5856572%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20Mumbai's%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20International%20Airport%2C%20two%20aircraft%20came%20alarmingly%20close%20to%20each%20other%20on%20the%20runway%20yesterday%2C%20with%20only%20509%20metres%20separating%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-mumbai-airport-scare-indigo-and-air-india-planes-were-just-509-m-apart-5856572%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-mumbai-airport-scare-indigo-and-air-india-planes-were-just-509-m-apart-5856572%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-mumbai-airport-scare-indigo-and-air-india-planes-were-just-509-m-apart-5856572%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20Modi%203.0's%20Seven%20Women%20Ministers%2C%20Two%20Of%20Them%20Hold%20Cabinet%20Rank%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%2072-member%20council%20of%20ministers%20in%20the%20third%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20seven%20women%2C%20including%20two%20with%20ca