%3D2146%26languageId%3D1%26contentId%3D84371%5C%22%3ERoyal%20Canadian%20Police%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20June%207%20at%208%3A46%20am%2C%20when%20the%20Surrey%20Police%20received%20a%20call%20reporting%20a%20shooting%20in%20the%20900-block%20of%20164%20Street%20in%20Surrey%2C%20British%20Columbia.%20Upon%20arrival%2C%20officers%20found%20Yuvraj%20dead.%20The%20police%20have%20taken%20four%20suspects%20under%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspects%2C%20Manvir%20Basram%20(23)%2C%20Sahib%20Basra%20(20)%2C%20and%20Harkirat%20Jhutty%20(23)%20of%20Surrey%2C%20and%20Keilon%20Francois%20(20)%20of%20Ontario%2C%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20first-degree%20murder%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20thankful%20for%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20the%20Surrey%20RCMP%2C%20Air%201%2C%20and%20%C2%A0Lower%20Mainland%20Integrated%20Emergency%20Response%20Team%20(IERT)%2C%20but%20there%20is%20still%20more%20work%20to%20be%20done.%20%C2%A0Integrated%20Homicide%20Investigation%20Team%20(IHIT)%20investigators%20remain%20dedicated%20to%20determining%20why%20Mr%20Goyal%20was%20the%20victim%20of%20this%20homicide%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sergeant%20Timothy%20Pierotti%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreliminary%20investigation%20into%20the%20case%20suggests%20that%20the%20shooting%20was%20targeted%2C%20although%20the%20reasons%20behind%20Yuvraj's%20killing%20are%20still%20being%20explored%2C%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717990620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fckrje5ng_yuvraj-goyal-_625x300_10_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-man-from-ludhiana-shot-dead-in-canada-targeted-killing-suspected-5856219%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Indian-origin%20man%20from%20Punjab's%20Ludhiana%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20Canada's%20Surrey%20on%20Friday.%20The%20victim%2C%20Yuvraj%20Goyal%2C%20arrived%20in%20Canada%20in%202019%20on