e%20for%20cricket%20and%20stated%20that%20the%20sport%20taught%20him%20teamwork%20and%20leadership%20that%20helped%20him%20rise%20through%20the%20twists%20and%20turns%20of%20the%20corporate%20world.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20playing%20cricket%20taught%20me%20more%20about%20working%20in%20teams%20and%20leadership%20that%20has%20stayed%20with%20me%20throughout%20my%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20after%20his%20appointment%20as%20Microsoft%20CEO%20was%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717990200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fdg30o94g_satya-nadella_625x300_10_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsuper-fan-satya-nadella-spotted-wearing-indian-jersey-at-india-vs-pakistan-match-5856448%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20did%20the%20improbable%20of%20defending%20a%20120-run%20target%20against%20Pakistan%20to%20notch%20a%20memorable%20win%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsuper-fan-satya-nadella-spotted-wearing-indian-jersey-at-india-vs-pakistan-match-5856448%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsuper-fan-satya-nadella-spotted-wearing-indian-jersey-at-india-vs-pakistan-match-5856448%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsuper-fan-satya-nadella-spotted-wearing-indian-jersey-at-india-vs-pakistan-match-5856448%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan't%20Expect%20Much%26quot%3B%3A%20Babar%20Doesn't%20Mince%20Words%2C%20Blames%20India%20Defeat%20On...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20side's%20six-run%20loss%20to%20India%20in%20their%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%20match%2C%20Pakistan%20skipper%20Babar%20Azam%20admitted%20that%20his%20side%20losing%20back-to-back%20wickets%20and%20playing%20more%20dot%20balls%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%20their%20innings%20contributed%20to%20their%20defeat%20despite%20a%20fine%20bowling%20performance.%20In%20a%20nerve-wracking%20battle%20between%20bat%20and%20ball%2C%20Pakistan%20could%20not%20hold%20their%20nerves%2C%20giving%20away%20a%20solid%20position%20after%20the%20first%20half%20while%20chasing%20120%20runs%20as%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%20pulled%20back%20the%20game%20with%20their%20bowling%20and%20left%20their%20opponents%20short%20by%20six%20runs%20at%20New%20York's%20Nassau%20County%20Stadium%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20the%20post-match%20presentation%2C%20Babar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20bowled%20well.%20In%20the%20batting%2C%20lost%20back-to-back%20wickets%20and%20had%20too%20many%20dot%20balls.%20Tactics%20were%20simple%20to%20play%20normally.%20Just%20strike%20rotation%20and%20the%20odd%20boundary.%20But%20in%20that%20period%20(the%20second%20half%20of%20their%20run-chase)%20we%20had%20too%20many%20dot%20balls.%20We%20cannot%20expect%20much%20from%20tailenders.%20Our%20mind%20was%20to%20utilise%20the%20first%20six%20overs%20in%20batting.%20But%20one%20wicket%20down%2C%20and%20again%20we%20were%20not%20up%20to%20the%20mark%20in%20that%20phase.%20The%20pitch%20looked%20decent.%20The%20ball%20was%20coming%20on%20nicely.%20It%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20slow%2C%20and%20some%20balls%20extra%20bounce.%20Have%20to%20win%20the%20last%20two%20matches.%20Will%20sit%20and%20discuss%20our%20mistakes%20but%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20last%20two%20matches.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20winning%20this%20thriller%2C%20India%20is%20at%20the%20top%20of%20Group%20A%20with%20two%20wins%20in%20two%20games%20and%20four%20points.%20Pakistan%20is%20in%20fourth%20place%2C%20having%20lost%20both%20their%20games%20to%20the%20USA%20and%20India.%20Their%20knockout%20stage%20chances%20look%20slim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20Pakistan%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20put%20India%20to%20bat%20first.%20However%2C%20the%20Indian%20batters%20did%20not%20get%20things%20going%20for%20them%20at%20this%20tough%20surface%20as%20star%20openers%20Virat%20Kohli%20(4)%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(13)%20failed%20to%20score%20big.%20Rishabh%20Pant%20(42%20in%2031%20balls%2C%20with%20six%20fours)%20seemed%20to%20be%20playing%20on%20a%20different%20pitch%20and%20had%20useful%20partnerships%20with%20Axar%20Patel%20(20%20in%2018%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20and%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20(seven%20in%20eight%20balls%2C%20with%20a%20four).%20However%2C%20the%20lower%20middle%20order%20crumbled%20under%20the%20pressure%20of%20scoring%20runs%20on%20such%20a%20tough%20pitch%20and%20India%20could%20make%20just%20119%20in%2019%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaris%20Rauf%20(3%2F21)%20and%20Naseem%20Shah%20(3%2F21)%20were%20the%20top%20bowlers%20for%20Pakistan.%20Mohammed%20Amir%20got%20two%20scalps%20while%20Shaheen%20Shah%20Afridi%20got%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run-chase%2C%20Pakistan%20took%20a%20more%20measured%20approach%20and%20Mohammed%20Rizwan%20(31%20in%2044%20balls%2C%20with%20a%20four%20and%20six)%20held%20one%20end%20steady.%20However%2C%20Bumrah%20(3%2F14)%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%20(2%2F24)%20got%20crucial%20wickets%20of%20skipper%20Babar%20Azam%20(13)%2C%20Fakhar%20Zaman%20(13)%2C%20Shadab%20Khan%20(4)%2C%20Iftikhar%20Ahmed%20(5)%20as%20well%2C%20which%20kept%20the%20pressure%20intact%20on%20Pakistan.%20With%2018%20runs%20needed%20in%20the%20final%20over%2C%20Naseem%20Shah%20(10*)%20tried%20to%20win%20it%20for%20Pakistan%2C%20however%2C%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20(1%2F31)%20made%20sure%20Pakistan%20fell%20short%20by%20six%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20secured%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20for%20his%20match-winning%20spell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A171799014000