aign%20for%20the%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20till%20now%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Babar%20Azam%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59905-mohammad-babar-azam-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBabar%20Azam%3C%2Fa%3E-led%20side%20slumped%20to%20a%206-run%20loss%20against%20India%20on%20Sunday.%20It%20was%20the%20second%20defeat%20for%20Pakistan%20in%20two%20matches%20after%20they%20were%20stunned%20by%20United%20States%20in%20the%20first%20group%20stage%20encounter.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Naseem%20Shah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112320-naseem-shah-playerprofile%5C%22%3ENaseem%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Haris%20Rauf%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112775-haris-rauf-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHaris%20Rauf%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20three%20wickets%20each%20to%20bundle%20out%20India%20for%20119%20but%20a%20disciplined%20show%20from%20India%20pacers%2C%20specially%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20handed%20Pakistan%20a%20crushing%20defeat.%20The%20loss%20against%20India%20was%20also%20a%20huge%20blow%20for%20Pakistan's%20chances%20of%20reaching%20the%20Super%208%20stage%20of%20the%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20have%200%20points%20after%202%20matches%20and%20their%20qualification%20chances%20are%20looking%20quite%20slim%20at%20the%20moment.%20The%20Babar%20Azam-led%20side%20will%20have%20to%20win%20their%20two%20remaining%20matches%20against%20Canada%20and%20Ireland%20while%20hoping%20that%20United%20States%20and%20Canada%20do%20not%20win%20any%20more%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20Pakistan%20win%20both%20of%20their%20matches%20and%20United%20States%20lose%20their%20two%20remaining%20games%2C%20the%20qualification%20to%20the%20Super%208%20stage%20will%20come%20down%20to%20Net%20Run%20Rate%20(NRR).%20Both%20sides%20will%20have%204%20points%20from%204%20matches%20and%20Pakistan%20will%20need%20several%20results%20to%20go%20their%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20speedster%20Jasprit%20Bumah%2C%20who%20was%20named%20the%20player%20of%20the%20match%20after%20the%20game%2C%20truly%20cherished%20his%20performance%20against%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20really%20good.%20We%20felt%20we%20were%20a%20little%20under%20and%20the%20wicket%20got%20a%20little%20better%20after%20the%20sun%20came%20out.%20We%20were%20really%20disciplined%20so%20it%20feels%20good.%20Tried%20to%20hit%20the%20seam%20as%20much%20as%20I%20could%2C%20tried%20to%20be%20as%20clear%20as%20I%20could%20with%20my%20execution%20and%20it%20all%20came%20out%20well%20so%20I%20felt%20happy.%20Felt%20like%20we%20were%20playing%20in%20India%2C%20really%20happy%20with%20the%20support%20and%20that%20gives%20us%20energy%20on%20the%20field.%20We%20focus%20on%20the%20now.%20We've%20played%20two%20games%20and%20played%20really%20well.%20You%20stick%20to%20your%20processes%20and%20look%20to%20play%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Bumrah%20sai%20after%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717985940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fvvrpljv8_f_625x300_10_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fpakistan-out-of-t20-world-cup-2024-explaining-what-loss-vs-india-means-for-babar-azam-and-co-5855012%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20has%20been%20a%20disappointing%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20campaign%20for%20the%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20till%20now%20as%20the%20Babar%20Azam-led%20side%20slumped%20to%20a%206-run%20loss%20against%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fpakistan-out-of-t20-world-cup-2024-explaining-what-loss-vs-india-means-for-babar-azam-and-co-5855012%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F