22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63024-akshar-rajeshbhai-patel-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAxar%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20the%20only%20batters%20to%20show%20some%20promise%20as%20India%20were%20bundled%20out%20for%20119.%20The%20bowlers%20came%20to%20India's%20rescue%20as%20they%20produced%20a%20brilliant%20display%20to%20guide%20their%20team%20to%20a%20thrilling%20victory.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20bowlers%20as%20he%20finished%20with%203%20wickets.%20However%2C%20Rohit%20was%20not%20content%20with%20the%20victory%20and%20he%20went%20on%20to%20criticise%20how%20they%20batted%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20partnerships%20after%20a%20solid%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20bat%20well%20enough.%20Halfway%20through%20our%20innings%20we%20were%20in%20good%20position.%20We%20didn't%20put%20enough%20partnership%20there%20and%20fell%20short%20with%20the%20bat.%20We%20spoke%20about%20every%20run%20matters%20on%20a%20pitch%20like%20that.%20There%20was%20enough%20in%20the%20pitch.%20Was%20a%20good%20wicket%20to%20be%20honest%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20last%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Bumrah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20a%20bowling%20lineup%20like%20that%20you%20feel%20confident%20to%20do%20the%20job.%20Halfway%20through%20the%20stage%20when%20they%20were%20batting%2C%20we%20got%20everyone%20together%20and%20said%20that%20if%20it%20can%20happen%20to%20us%2C%20it%20can%20happen%20to%20them.%20Little%20contribution%20from%20everyone%20can%20make%20huge%20difference.%20He's%20going%20from%20strength%20to%20strength%20(Bumrah).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20know%20what%20he%20can%20do.%20Not%20going%20to%20talk%20too%20much%20about%20him.%20Want%20him%20to%20be%20in%20that%20mindset%20throughout%20the%20WC.%20He