tages%20from%20Gaza.%20In%20the%20clip%2C%20Almog%20Meir%20Jan%2C%20Shlomi%20Ziv%20and%20Andrey%20Kozlov%20can%20be%20seen%20running%20with%20the%20Israeli%20forces%20towards%20a%20stationed%20helicopter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20soon%20as%20the%20hostages%20along%20with%20the%20officers%20get%20into%20the%20chopper%20it%20takes%20off.%20The%20text%20in%20the%20clip%20reads%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20takeoff%20of%20the%20helicopter%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20with%20three%20of%20the%20rescued%20hostages.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20clip%20was%20shared%20along%20with%20the%20text%2C%20%E2%80%9CBringing%20them%20home%3A%20The%20moment%20we%20rescued%203%20of%20the%204%20hostages%20from%20the%20heart%20of%20Gaza.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EBringing%20them%20home%3A%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20moment%20we%20rescued%203%20of%20the%204%20hostages%20from%20the%20heart%20of%20Gaza.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FNkQvXJ9ChT%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FNkQvXJ9ChT%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(%40IDF)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIDF%2Fstatus%2F1799460733962555435%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMr%20Hagari%20informed%20that%20under%20100%20Palestinians%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20raid.%20These%20hostages%20were%20held%20captive%20in%20civilian%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20intelligence%20was%20able%20to%20pinpoint%20two%20of%20these%20buildings%20in%20Nuseirat%2C%20wherein%20families%20were%20staying%20with%20armed%20guards%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMr%20Hagari%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20huge%20risk%20because%20they%20might%20have%20thought%20that%20we%20were%20pre