of%20Monteverde%20quickly%20topped%20our%20list%20of%20things%20to%20do%20while%20we%20researched%20our%20trip.%20If%20I%20could%20have%20extended%20our%20stay%20longer%2C%20this%20is%20the%20one%20thing%20I'd%20want%20to%20do%20more%20of%2C%20mostly%20to%20see%20more%20of%20the%20incredible%20wildlife%20in%20the%20Puntarenas%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigh%20in%20the%20mountains%2C%20about%2030%20minutes%20from%20the%20artsy%20township%20of%20Santa%20Elena%2C%20we%20went%20on%20a%20self-guided%20hike%20to%20see%20the%20El%20Tigre%20Waterfalls.%20The%208-kilometer%20hike%20takes%20you%20through%20a%20humid%20jungle%20over%20several%20hanging%20bridges%20and%20offers%20stunning%20views%20of%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20waterfalls%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20animals%20were%20the%20highlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20saw%20massive%20butterflies%2C%20multiple%20species%20of%20hummingbirds%20and%20frogs%2C%20a%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etoucan%2C%20motmots%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F13ft-python-survived-months-eating-cats-oklahoma-trailer-park-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econcerningly%20large%20snake%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20glimpses%20of%20monkeys%20in%20the%20branches%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20from%20a%20hanging%20bridge%20at%20El%20Tigre%20Waterfalls%2C%20a%20hiking%20spot%20near%20Santa%20Elena%2C%20Costa%20Rica.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6664ca1ea2a35d0ca3770eec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222924%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEl%20Tigre%20offered%20us%20some%20of%20the%20best%20hiking%20we%20experienced%20in%20Costa%20Rica%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20a%20chance%20to%20see%20diverse%20wildlife%20like%20snakes%2C%20monkeys%2C%20and%20motmots%20as%20we%20explored%20the%20jungle.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20the%20cooler%20month%20of%20May%2C%20it%