www.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-openai-researcher-leopold-aschenbrenner-interview-firing-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20shared%20was%20%26quot%3Btotally%20normal%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20OpenAI%20may%20have%20just%20been%20looking%20for%20a%20reason%20to%20fire%20him.%20He%20was%20one%20of%20several%20employees%20who%20refused%20to%20sign%20a%20letter%20calling%20for%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman's%20return%20after%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-sam-altman-did-so-bad-he-got-fired-openai-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboard%20briefly%20ousted%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAschenbrenner's%20essay%20doesn't%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eappear%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Einclude%20sensitive%20details%20about%20OpenAI.%20Instead%2C%20as%20Aschenbrenner%20writes%20on%20the%20dedication%20page%2C%20it's%20based%20on%20%26quot%3Bpublicly%20available%20information%2C%20my%20own%20ideas%2C%20general%20field%20knowledge%2C%20or%20SF%20gossip.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20uploaded%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20tract%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgpt-4-predict-company-future-performance-better-than-humans-study-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20GPT-4%20model%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20asked%20it%20to%20summarize%20the%20work%20and%20relay%20the%20most%20significant%20takeaways.%20We%20also%20gently%20requested%20that%20the%20bot%20keep%20its%20summary%20clear%20and%20concise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b88f2780-5d22-4c4c-8428-83970bb3e31c%5C%22%3EHere's%20ChatGPT's%2057-word%20summary%20of%20Aschenbrenner's%20essay%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20distilled%20the%20essay%20into%2057%20words%20that%20outlined%20Aschenbrenner's%20views%20on%20the%20evolution%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLeopold%20Aschenbrenner's%20essay%20discusses%20the%20transformative%20potential%20of%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%20(AGI)%20and%20superintelligence%2C%20and%20forecasts%20significant%20advancements%20in%20AI%20technology%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20Aschenbrenner%2C%20formerly%20associated%20with%20OpenAI%2C%20outlines%20how%20the%20progression%20from%20current%20AI%20models%20like%20GPT-4%20to%20AGI%20could%20occur%20much%20faster%20than%20anticipated%2C%20based%20on%20trends%20in%20computational%20power%20and%20algorithmic%20efficiency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc3b086a-84bd-42f2-ba2a-3e4966c22a5a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChatGPT%20then%20offered%20four%20key%20takeaways%20from%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAschenbrenner's%20essay%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERapid%20Progress%20in%20AI%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAschenbrenner%20argues%20that%20AI%20development%20is%20accelerating%20at%20an%20unprecedented%20rate.%20He%20predicts%20that%20by%202027%2C%20AI%20models%20could%20reach%20the%20capabilities%20of%20human%20AI%20researchers%20and%20engineers%2C%20potentially%20leading%20to%20an%20intelligence%20explosion%20where%20AI%20surpasses%20human%20intelligence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEconomic%20and%20Security%20Implications%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20essay%20highlights%20the%20immense%20economic%20and%20security%20implications%20of%20these%20advancements.%20Aschenbrenner%20points%20out%20that%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20are%20being%20invested%20into%20developing%20the%20infrastructure%20needed%20to%20support%20these%20AI%20systems%2C%20such%20as%20GPUs%2C%20data%20centers%2C%20and%20power%20generation.%20He%20also%20emphasizes%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20securing%20these%20technologies%20to%20prevent%20misuse%2C%20particularly%20by%20state%20actors%20like%20the%20CCP.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETechnical%20and%20Ethical%20Challenges%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechnical%20and%20Ethical%20Challenges%3A%20The%20essay%20discusses%20the%20significant%20challenges%20in%20controlling%20AI%20systems%20smarter%20than%20humans%2C%20referring%20to%20this%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bsuperalignment%26quot%3B%20problem.%20Managing%20this%20will%20be%20crucial%20to%20prevent%20catastrophic%20outcomes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPredictions%20and%20Societal%20Impact%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAschenbrenner%20suggests%20that%20few%20people%20truly%20understand%20the%20scale%20of%20change%20that%20AI%20is%20about%20to%20bring.%20He%20discusses%20the%20potential%20for%20AI%20to%20reshape%20industries%2C%20enhance%20national%20security%2C%20and%20pose%20new%20ethical%20and%20governance%20challenges.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bc7511d7-b3bc-474f-b1d0-d24d83b5f4a6%5C%22%3EThere's%20more.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Aschenbrenner%20wrote%2C%20there%20are%20probably%20only%20a%20few%20hundred%20people%2C%20most%20of%20them%20in%20AI%20labs%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20who%20have%20%26quot%3Bsituational%20awareness%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20industry.%20These%20people%20will%20likely%20have%20the%20best%20insight%20into%20how%20AI%20will%20reshape%20the%20years%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAschenbrenner%2C%20as%20one%20of%20them%2C%20seems%20to%20believe%20AI%20will%20assume%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20followed%20up%20our%20original%20prompt%20by%20asking%20ChatGPT%20to%20summarize%20the%20predictions%20Aschenbrenner%20made%20in%20his%20essay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20ChatGPT%20broke%20it%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAGI%20by%202027%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BAschenbrenner%20predicts%20that%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%20(AGI)%20is%20strikingly%20plausible%20by%202027%2C%20highlighting%20the%20rapid%20progress%20from%20GPT-2%20to%20GPT-4%2C%20which%20saw%20AI%20models%20advancing%20from%20preschool-level%20to%20smart%20high-schooler%20abilities%20in%20just%20four%20years.%20He%20expects%20a%20similar%20leap%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years%20based%20on%20consistent%20improvements%20in%20compute%20and%20algorithmic%20efficiency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuperintelligence%20Following%20AGI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BPost-AGI%2C%20the%20author%20anticipates%20an%20%26quot%3Bintelligence%20explosion%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20AI%20rapidly%20advances%20from%20human-level%20to%20superhuman%20capabilities.%20This%20transition%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20fueled%20by%20AI's%20ability%20to%20automate%20and%20accelerate%20its%20own%20research%20and%20development.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrillion-Dollar%20AI%20Clusters%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BEconomically%2C%20Aschenbrenner%20suggests%20that%20the%20AI%20sector%20will%20see%20an%20increase%20in%20investment%20into%20trillion-dollar%20compute%20clusters%20as%20corporations%20and%20governments%20prepare%20for%20the%20implications%20of%20AGI%20and%20superintelligence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENational%20and%20Global%20Security%20Dynamics%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20predictions%20about%20intense%20national%20security%20measures%20being%20enacted%20to%20manage%20and%20control%20AI%20developments.%20The%20competition%2C%20particularly%20with%20the%20Chinese%20government%2C%20could%20intensify%2C%20possibly%20leading%20to%20an%20'all-out%20war'%20if%20not%20managed%20properly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuperalignment%20Challenges%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20most%20critical%20predictions%20is%20the%20struggle%20with%20'superalignment'%20%E2%80%94%20the%20challenge%20of%20keeping%20superintelligent%20AI%20aligned%20with%20human%20values%20and%20interests.%20This%20problem%20is%20anticipated%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20central%20hurdles%20as%20AI%20reaches%20and%20surpasses%20human%20intelligence%20levels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESocietal%20and%20Economic%20Transformations%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BAschenbrenner%20expects%20AI%20to%20have%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20society%20and