0replace%20them%20multiple%20times%20which%20would%20increase%20your%20cost%20capital%20tremendously.%20Opt%20for%20inverters%20with%20a%20replacement%20warranty%20of%2010%20years%20so%20that%20you%20only%20replace%20it%20once.%20While%20this%20would%20cost%20you%20an%20additional%20Rs%201%20lakh%2C%20it%20will%20save%20you%20on%20recurring%20battery%20replacement%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBird%20droppings%20obstruct%20the%20sunlight%20that%20solar%20panels%20require%20to%20generate%20power.%20Therefore%2C%20you%20must%20routinely%20remove%20bird%20droppings%20from%20your%20solar%20setup.%20Install%20transponders%20that%20will%20transmit%20the%20live%20readings%20to%20you%20and%20show%20which%20panel%20is%20not%20generating%20enough%20electricity.%20Immediately%2C%20clean%20the%20panel%20to%20avoid%20malfunctions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%226%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDepending%20on%20the%20shadow%20analysis%2C%20you%20can%20recover%20the%20investment%20costs%20in%204-6%20years%20from%20the%20year%20of%20solar%20installation.%20Once%20you%20get%20your%20return%20on%20investment%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20get%20free%20power.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%227%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApartment%20owners%20or%20tenants%20can%20install%20solar%20panels%20on%20their%20balconies%20provided%20they%20receive%20sufficient%20sunlight.%20A%20person%20living%20on%20the%20second%20floor%20and%2020th%20floor%20will%20receive%20different%20amounts%20of%20sunlight.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20building%20surrounding%20your%20view%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20sunlight%2C%20then%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20viable%20option%20as%20the%20efficiency%20levels%20will%20reduce.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%228%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EConsider%20the%20area%20of%20coverage%20on%20your%20balcony.%20If%20your%20balcony%20is%2012-feet%20long%2C%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20place%203-4%20panels.%