20that%20makes%20plastic-like%20items%20using%20sugarcane.%20Their%20products%20are%20biodegradable%20and%20decompose%20in%20180%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Villages%20to%20Cities%3A%20How%20Coca-Cola%20Uses%20Coolers%20to%20Transform%20Businesses%20for%20Indian%20Retailers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20sponsored%20by%20Coca-Cola%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20a%20regular%20refrigerator.%20However%2C%20Coca-Cola%E2%80%99s%20coolers%2C%20easily%20recognisable%20by%20their%20red%20and%20white%20design%2C%20stocked%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20beverages%2C%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20common%20in%20India.%20We%20are%20not%20just%20talking%20about%20their%20growing%20visibility%20across%20cities%20but%20through%20the%20towns%20to%20the%20villages%2C%20where%20these%20coolers%20stand%20tall%20in%20kiranas%2C%20hotel%20corners%2C%20or%20retail%20aisles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20vast%20network%20of%20providing%20beverages%20to%20over%205%20million%20outlets%20across%20the%20country%2C%20Coca-Cola%20is%20expanding%20the%20presence%20of%20its%20coolers%20to%20every%20corner%20of%20India.%20With%20India%20achieving%20100%20percent%20electrification%20of%20villages%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekiranas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20fast-growing%20network%20of%20small%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20large%20retailers%20now%20effortlessly%20use%20the%20Coca-Cola%20coolers%20as%20part%20of%20their%20shop%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20bringing%20to%20reality%20what%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20former%20president%20Robert%20Woodruff%20famously%20said%20about%20winning%20in%20the%20beverage%20market%20%E2%80%94%20delivering%20its%20products%20%E2%80%9Cwithin%20an%20arm%E2%80%99s%20reach%20of%20desire%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20any%20desire%3A%20The%20desire%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F293356%2Fhealth-benefits-of-kanji-fermented-rice-water-ancient-south-india-food-science%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecool%2C%20refreshing%20beverage%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20any%20occasion%20%E2%80%94%20after%20a%20delightful%20lunch%2C%20an%20exciting%20evening%20of%20cricket%2C%20or%20a%20quick%20gulp%20after%20a%20shopping%20stroll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBoosting%20retailer%20revenue%20and%20consumer%20experience%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoca-Cola%E2%80%99s%20coolers%20are%20now%20contributing%20to%20increased%20revenues%20for%20retailers%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20micro%2C%20small%2C%20and%20medium%20players%2C%20many%20of%20them%20having%20access%20to%20coolers%20following%20the%20electrification%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20consumers%2C%20the%20benefits%20are%20evident%3A%20Not%20only%20do%20they%20have%20a%20chilled%20beverage%2C%20but%20they%20are%20also%20assured%20of%20its%20purity%20and%20hygiene.%20They%20also%20present%20them%20with%20an%20array%20of%20options%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20diversity%20that%20a%20Coca-Cola%20cooler%2C%20with%20exclusive%20rack%20space%20for%20its%20products%2C%20provides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20retailers%2C%20the%20benefits%20are%20manifold.%20One%2C%20the%20advent%20of%20more%20coolers%2C%20especially%20in%20remote%20areas%2C%20has%20helped%20attract%20new%20consumers%2C%20increasing%20their%20share%20of%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297294%2Fhistory-origin-of-south-india-iconic-drinks-filter-coffee-jigarthanda-tamil-nadu-kerala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enon-alcoholic%20beverages%3C%2Fa%3E%20market%20is%20growing%20at%20a%20CAGR%20of%208.7%20percent%20to%20INR%201%2C47%2C233%20crores%20by%202030%2C