ave%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Moved%20To%20Delhi%20With%20Rs%201200%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20Man%E2%80%99s%20Startup%20Dream%20%26amp%3B%20a%20Popsicle%20Biz%20That%20Earns%20Rs%208%20Crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20bell%20of%20the%20ice-cream%20seller%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20anticipated%20sounds%20in%20most%20of%20our%20childhoods.%20As%20soon%20as%20Gagan%20Anand%20would%20hear%20the%20bell%20back%20in%20the%2090s%2C%20he%20would%20rush%20to%20his%20mother%20to%20borrow%20Re%201%2C%20run%20behind%20the%20ice-cream%20man%20down%20the%20roads%20of%20Jharkhand%20(then%20Bihar).%20Other%20summer%20treats%20included%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98barf-ka-gola%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(snowcones).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F349369%2Fsiri-millet-vegan-ice-cream-trichy-non-dairy-healthy-frozen-dessert%2F%5C%22%3Elove%20for%20ice-creams%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ice-candy%20and%20%3Cem%3Egola%20%3C%2Fem%3Econtinued%20well%20into%20his%20adulthood%2C%20and%20became%20%E2%80%98all-weather%20friends%E2%80%99%20for%20the%2037-year-old.%20He%20rose%20from%20being%20a%20team%20member%20at%20Pizza%20Hut%20to%20managing%20big%20brands%20like%20Gloria%20Jeans%20Coffee%20and%20Rasna%2C%20and%20now%20runs%20a%20successful%20ice-cream%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20youngest%20of%20four%20siblings%2C%20Gagan%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20middle-class%20home%20with%20lofty%20dreams%20of%20becoming%20an%20actor.%20However%2C%20his%20father%20retired%20when%20he%20had%20just%20completed%20Class%2010%2C%20which%20propelled%20him%20towards%20making%20his%20own%20life%20through%20sheer%20hard%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Rs%201%2C200%20in%20his%20pocket%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20New%20Delhi%20to%20pursue%20acting%20at%20just%2016.%20He%20soon%20realised%20that%20making%20a%20name%20for%20yourself%20in%20this%20field%20was%20rather%20difficult.%20Roaming%20around%20Co